# Wiki specific - sources are user-managed, not versioned by default
# Reason: original materials can be large (PDFs, videos, archives)
# and are often managed separately (cloud storage, reference managers)
#
# If you want to version small text files in sources/, use:
#   !sources/*.md
#   !sources/*.txt
#
sources/*
!sources/README.md
!sources/.gitkeep

